{"tid":698742,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國中妹要媽帶她看性病　結果慘的是男友","createTime":"2018-06-12T03:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T13:33:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"35fadb9da41f47058348055660c9868d4385fd08","tid":698742,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:27:40.000Z","msg":"新北市一名13歲國中妹2016年4月下體不舒服，懷疑遭21歲林姓男友傳染性病，只好向母親坦承與男友3次嘿咻，請母親帶她去診所看病，結果醫師診斷少女罹患披衣菌疾病，與性行為無關，卻因此揭發男友觸犯與未滿14歲少女性交罪。新北地院昨判林男3年4月徒刑。<br />\n判決指出，林男（23歲）2014年間經由被害少女的表哥介紹認識少女，2016年2月跟當時年僅13歲、就讀國中2年級的少女交往。同年3月少女3次放學前往林男的三重住家，兩人先在客廳聊天，隨後進房改在床上聊，林男打情罵俏要求嘿咻，少女也未拒絕，因而發生性行為。<br />\n隔月，少女下體不舒服，且知林男經常小便疼痛，擔心自己罹患性病，才跟母親提起有跟男友性行為，要母親帶她去診所看病，母親才驚覺女兒遭性侵，憤而報警。<br />\n事後少女由母親帶往醫院接受性侵害驗傷檢查，確認有陳舊性裂傷，至於少女下體不適的原因，醫師診斷認定感染披衣菌，與林男的尿道炎無關，但林男仍被依與未成年少女性交罪起訴。<br />\n新北地院審理時，林男一開始坦承犯行，後來翻供否認有跟少女嘿咻，辯稱那三天他都被派遣公司派往工地工作，根本不在家，但因林男的派遣公司提供記錄顯示，那三天都沒有派遣林男工作的記錄，因此不採信林男辯詞，昨判林男有罪。仍可上訴。（孫友廉／新北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/112714_be09f468f0bbc6ce10799631f8ec3316.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F112714_be09f468f0bbc6ce10799631f8ec3316.png&h=dc1919ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180612/1371214\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180612%2F1371214&d=hkHU0MedtjLmZEcdjw3s7o9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=66cda18c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180612%2F1371214&h=0d86db02\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180612/1371214</a>"},{"pid":"1ecce7fafb0e4ed63fd42245d3de9119cdb1dec0","tid":698742,"uid":77904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"所以話"},{"pid":"d16be1e455d06c2556fd6b97b4b8eb761106fc28","tid":698742,"uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ecce7fafb0e4ed63fd42245d3de9119cdb1dec0","tid":698742,"uid":77904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"所以話"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"台灣"},{"pid":"54b7e940674c54a7067871600bc407e4390dad85","tid":698742,"uid":157765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"goal<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc24c1ba4c0dc5bed9d19bb2a1ffcbbe124938bc","tid":698742,"uid":55924,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:54:35.000Z","msg":"00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae11c5f71361d9998edf3fa291251982af283e6e","tid":698742,"uid":130456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:58:22.000Z","msg":"自願同人啪啪啪 但又講到個女俾人性侵 goodest logic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bee595439bf051b092bb2d11f8ffd542c568ec04","tid":698742,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54b7e940674c54a7067871600bc407e4390dad85","tid":698742,"uid":157765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"goal<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T12:59:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb63491df906176791a0e3cefa56537866ce14dc","tid":698742,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T13:20:38.000Z","msg":"metoo"},{"pid":"246725d9f31d3198901a1ab584441110ebac20a4","tid":698742,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"文章頭兩個字就係重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}